T02D2733b:112a-0: @112a # // thugs rje chen po 'phags pa spyan @112b ras gzigs //
T02D2733b:112a-1: 'gro la nye ring med pas khyad du 'phags //
T02D2733b:112a-2: sems can rnams la spyan ras gzigs mdzod la //
T02D2733b:112a-3: kun gyis rang ngo shes par byin gyis rlobs //
T02D2733b:112a-4: rang don du chos sku rtogs pa //
T02D2733b:112a-5: gzhan don du gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis kyis /
T02D2733b:112a-6: mthong thos dran reg gi sgo nas /
T02D2733b:112a-7: 'gro ba yongs la pan thogs pa /
T02D2733b:112a-8: 'gro ba yongs kyi don rlabs po che 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
T02D2733b:112a-9: na mo ratna tra y'a ya /
T02D2733b:112a-10: nam a'ary'a ba lo ki te shva r'a ya /
T02D2733b:112a-13: ma h'a k'a ru ni k'a ya /
T02D2733b:112a-17: ma h'a padma ru ru tishtha /
T02D2733b:112a-22: aom padma tsint'a ma ni dzva lah'um /
T02D2733b:112a-24: aom bha ra ta padme h'um /
